  <summary>2/27/1997--Introduced.
Domestic Violence Identification and Referral Act of 1997 - Amends the Public Health Service Act to give preference, in making grants or contracts under provisions relating to health professions education and provisions relating to nurse education, to certain health professions entities that train students in the identification, examination, treatment, and referral of victims of domestic violence.</summary>
